'''Masi Oka''' is a former employee of [[Industrial Light & Magic]], where he was a digital and visual effects artist working on the [[Prequel trilogy|Star Wars prequels]]. He was responsible for the effects involved in creating [[Geonosis/Legends|Geonosis's]] rings in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']].

Oka is also an actor; he starred in the NBC television series [[Wikipedia:Heroes (TV series)|''Heroes'']] as the time and space-bending Hiro Nakamura.

